{
  "stem": "6763.4",
  "chunk_idx": 3,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And nobody was nervous because nobody knew.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And I slept on it.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "[LAUGHS]",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Ljubljana was another game.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "That was totally different.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "There we-- [SIGHS] my mother must have sold some more jewels.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And we lived in an apartment building and shared an apartment with some Slovenian people who sublet a room, kitchen facilities, something like that.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And the communists were the big problem there for the Italians.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "They were fighting the Italians.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And they used to kidnap officers, soldiers, what have you, and kill them.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And the Italians retaliated by making house searches from top to bottom.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And when I say a house search, they would arrive at a house, at a building, they would surround the corner of the whole block, and then go from room to room, smash pillars, walls, to feel if there were any arms, any literature-- communist literature-- anybody hidden, and search for whoever their enemy was at that time.",
      "word_count": 58
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And they took my father and brother away as hostages 19 times.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And what they did was they took-- they surren-- they rounded up hostages.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And for any number-- let's say an officer was 25 hostages that was shot.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "They had numbers, they had value numbers on whether it was a-- a private, or it was a soldier, or it was.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And the higher the rank, the higher the number of people.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "So.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And they stamped it into the papers.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "They had a paper and they stamped each time they took you away.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And they were gone 19 times.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And 19 times we didn't know if we were ever going to see them again.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And that was horrible.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "It was just-- I mean to see my father being dragged away, it was just terrible.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "That-- I can't tell exactly how long we were there.",
      "word_count": 10
    }
  ],
